## 🎯 Accuracy & Auto-Hedging Engine

The Story Graph's `[Verified]` / `[Speculative]` node distribution directly controls narrative tone and C2PA disclaimer injection.

### Accuracy Threshold Matrix
| Speculative Ratio | Pipeline Behavior | C2PA Disclaimer |
|-------------------|-------------------|-----------------|
| $\le 0.15$ | `accuracy_mode: verified_only` | None required |
| $0.16 \text{--} 0.45$ | `accuracy_mode: speculative_inline` | `[Speculative Interpretation]` watermark + narrator hedging |
| $\ge 0.46$ | `accuracy_mode: creative_fiction` | `[Mythic/Adapted Narrative]` persistent badge |

### SDK Hedging Injection
```python
def apply_accuracy_hedging(script_text: str, speculative_ratio: float) -> str:
    if speculative_ratio > 0.45:
        prefix = "⚠️ Note: This narrative draws from adapted mythological sources.\n"
        return prefix + replace_late_claims_with_hedges(script_text)
    return script_text
```

