## ♿ Accessibility & WCAG 2.2 Gate

The `export_video` stage enforces accessibility compliance before artifact finalization.

| Check | Tool/Validator | Pass Criteria |
|-------|----------------|---------------|
| **Caption Sync** | `webvtt-validator` | $< 150\text{ms}$ drift from audio peaks |
| **Audio Description** | `ad_track_analyzer` | Covers $100\%$ of silent narrative gaps |
| **Text Contrast** | `axe-core` (headless) | $\ge 4.5:1$ ratio for legends/disclaimers |
| **Safe Zone** | `subtitle_layout_checker` | Within $90\%$ title-safe region |

**CI Enforcement:**
```yaml
- name: 🧪 WCAG Compliance Check
  run: |
    pip install aethel-compliance-tools
    aethelcompliance wcag --input ./aethel_output/render.mp4 --level AA
```

