## 🚪 CI/CD Compliance Gates

Add these steps to your GitHub Actions workflow to block non-compliant renders before GPU consumption.

```yaml
# .github/workflows/aethel-compliance.yml
jobs:
  compliance-gate:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with: { python-version: '3.11' }
      - run: pip install aethel-sdk aethel-compliance-tools

      - name: 🔍 Validate Consent & Licenses
        run: aethelcompliance rights scan --payload config/pipeline.json --registry ./rights_registry.json

      - name: 📊 Accuracy Threshold Check
        run: |
          aethelcompliance accuracy check --graph data/story_graph.json
          # Fails if speculative_ratio > threshold defined in policy.json

      - name: 📜 C2PA Manifest Pre-Validation
        run: aethelcompliance c2pa verify --dry-run --template config/c2pa_policy.json
```

