## 📊 Enterprise Best Practices

| Practice | Implementation |
|----------|----------------|
| **Key Rotation** | C2PA signing keys rotate quarterly. Old manifests remain verifiable via archived public keys. |
| **Immutable Audit Logs** | All compliance decisions are hashed and appended to a Merkle tree. Queryable via `aethelcli audit --job-id <id>`. |
| **Policy-as-Code** | Store compliance rules in `config/compliance_policy.yaml`. CI gates fail if payload deviates. |
| **Right-to-Be-Forgotten** | `clone_consent_hash` registry supports revocation tags. Revoked hashes auto-block future renders using that voice profile. |
| **Regional Compliance** | Toggle `policy_region` in CI (`EU`, `US`, `APAC`) to adjust GDPR/Fair Use/WCAG strictness automatically. |

